File libsrc/libgobject/cssObjects.c

All new CssTable object structures must start with these elements. 
  typedef struct
  {
 	GObjectPart	core
 	CssTablePart	css;
  } *CssTable;
 
  typedef strct
  {
 	int		type;
 	int		name;
 	int		num_members;
 	CssDescription	*des;
 	int		num_bytes;
 	int		line_length;
  } *CssTablePart;
